          The PACK function
          The PACK function
          The PACK function
          The PACK function
ç          _________________
 
ç          The  PACK  function  creates  archives a group of CMS files.
ç          The archives may be written to disk, tape,  or  the  virtual
ç          punch or printer.
 
ç          –◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊Ø
