          The UNPACK Function
          The UNPACK Function
          The UNPACK Function
          The UNPACK Function
ç          ___________________
 
ç          The UNPACK function extracts CMS files from archives created
ç          by  the  PACK function.  The archives can be read from tape,
ç          the reader, or from disk files.
 
ç          –◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊◊Ø
