ç          Previous  releases  of VMARC supported four additional func-
ç          tions.  These have since been superceded by options that may
ç          be used with the PACK and UNPACK functions.    However,  for
ç          compatibility  with  the earlier releases, VMARC accepts the
ç          older command syntax.  This support may be removed in future
ç          releases of VMARC, so users are advised not to depend on the
ç          older commands.
 
